1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:06,648
WindWalker turns a natural-language business request
into a deployed small-business web app.

2
00:00:06,648 --> 00:00:17,472
English digital-content bookstore: member login, cart,
test checkout, purchase history, downloads, and a seller dashboard.

3
00:00:17,472 --> 00:00:26,136
The builder generates a responsive app preview beside the conversation.
That same artifact is used for deployment.

4
00:00:26,136 --> 00:00:31,464
Deploy from the builder and open the live Cloudflare Pages URL.

5
00:00:31,464 --> 00:00:38,496
Mock login closes the dialog and changes the header
into the buyer account.

6
00:00:38,496 --> 00:00:46,608
Browse the catalog, open the cart, and arrive at test checkout.
No real payment is charged.

7
00:00:46,608 --> 00:00:57,480
GPT-5.6 supported final iteration and validation.
OpenAI Codex supported implementation, testing, and submission evidence.
